<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="1"><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Please do not respond to this email. This email was sent from an unattended mailbox, and replies are not reviewed. Please instead contact your Staffing representative on&nbsp;</b><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 18px;"><b>{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</b></span></font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="line-height: 18px;"><font size="2"><br></font></span></b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Dear&nbsp;</font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Job_placement__c.Contact_Name__c}</font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">,</font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Payment notification for NCS: PC, NCS: TC and NCS: RCD.</b></font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font size="2">We hope that you enjoyed your role on NCS with The Challenge.</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font size="2"><br></font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">You will receive your pay for&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Job_placement__c.Wave__c}</span><span style="font-family: Arial; line-height: 13.5909090042114px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"> on </span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Job_placement__c.Payroll_payment_date__c}.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">This pay constitutes your work between the dates of&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: Arial; line-height: 13.5909090042114px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Job_placement__c.Assignment_start_date__c} and {!Job_placement__c.Assignment_end_date__c} for </span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Job_placement__c.Wave__c}.&nbsp;</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2"><br></font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><font face="arial" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;">Your full gross pay for this part of the role is&nbsp;</font><font face="arial">{!Job_placement__c.Total_Amount_to_Pay__c}</font><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial;">.&nbsp;</font><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="line-height: 13.5909090042114px; white-space: pre-wrap;">This payment covers a total of&nbsp;</span></font></font></div><div><font size="2"><font face="Arial" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="line-height: 13.5909090042114px; white-space: pre-wrap;">  </span></font><font face="Arial"><span style="line-height: 13.5909090042114px; white-space: pre-wrap;">{!Job_placement__c.days_worked__c}&nbsp;</span></font><span style="font-family: arial; line-height: 13.5909090042114px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">working days</span><font face="Arial"><span style="line-height: 13.5909090042114px; white-space: pre-wrap;">. </span></font><span style="font-family: arial;">This is subject to tax and National Insurance contributions.&nbsp;</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">If you are involved in working on the NCS: Real Challenge Action and/or NCS: Graduation for the autumn programme, you will receive further payments through our later payrolls.</font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">On your payslip&nbsp;</span><font face="Arial, sans-serif">(sent via email on&nbsp;</font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">{!Job_placement__c.Payroll_payment_date__c})</span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">, you will see the total amount which you will receive.&nbsp;</span></font></p><p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></p><div style="font-family: arial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font face="arial" size="2">Due to new auto-</font><font size="2">enrolment</font><font face="arial" size="2">&nbsp;legislation, employees of The Challenge, including seasonal staff, may be enrolled in a workplace pension scheme. This is a way of saving for your retirement that's arranged by your employer.&nbsp;</font></font><font face="arial" size="2">For further information, please go to&nbsp;</font><a href="http://www.gov.uk/workplace-pensions" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); font-size: 13.3333330154419px;">www.gov.uk/workplace-<wbr>pensions</a><font face="arial" size="2">.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><font face="arial" size="2">&nbsp;</font></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333330154419px;">Further information about workplace pensions and how to opt-out can be found on the staffing website under FAQs.&nbsp;</span></div></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">If you have any questions please let us know</font></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;quoting the email reference number in any correspondence.</span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Yours sincerely,</font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">NCS with The Challenge</font></font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="line-height: 18px;">{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: left;"